mal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\nD蝨唔咬佢先最過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n成日半夜都要搽無比滴又怕會整醒佢"},{"pid":"2152474220cbc6f651ecb0435e8cfd00c753ad7f","tid":470182,"uid":118351,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:14:42.000Z","msg":"你搞清楚係bedbug定跳蚤先 兩樣嘢嚟"},{"pid":"8625708838bbfce29c0770d9d2bb4eb42f3e2ba0","tid":470182,"uid":24970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-16T06:20:02.000Z","msg":"如果係Bedbugs就準備好長期抗戰同換床啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n利申：同呢隻火星異種作戰過"},{"pid":"79d7e924542bd20509a8d37e3d45c397ed443d9f","tid":470182,"uid":968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T05:39:12.000Z","msg":"其實係咪分體質<br />\n我女朋友訓我張床無野咬<br />\n但我晚晚都比野咬"},{"pid":"e398721258e7a5ce08541b12ce1380e67c09351b","tid":470182,"uid":103342,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T19:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實係咪分體質<br />\n我女朋友訓我張床無野咬<br />\n但我晚晚都比野咬</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n體質就唔知 個人覺得容唔容易<br />\n被野咬（以木蝨為例）睇兩樣野<br />\n1.個人二氧化碳排放量<br />\n2.個人身體訊息<br />\n（例如：體溫熱可能吸引啲）<br />\n<br />\n你所講既體質 應該係咬後的反應<br />\n比較有關係 有啲被咬後的反應大<br />\n有啲相對較細 甚至無反應"},{"pid":"4382e5660e7f7d7562a0171c3d1e403f84ecb3d8","tid":470182,"uid":56328,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:03:02.000Z","msg":"你霸人張床梗咬你啦"},{"pid":"8b11de281a79a14c454b9eaa1db6cf46bea99c86","tid":470182,"uid":79839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:05:28.000Z","msg":"隨時帶番屋企<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ee062207ca401951e3be01ece2784e395131ad9","tid":470182,"uid":60434,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-19T20:34:32.000Z","msg":"點知係咩種類既？"}]}